original_title: Sorry You're Watching This: Faye Jackson
overview: CREEPSQUAD in the house! Dan Barry and special guest host, Juba are joined by the lovely Faye Jackson!  This in depth interview covers how Dan Barry ended her in ring career, as well as the freakiness of Faye!  Plus bonus matches from Queens Of Combat!  Faye & Willow VS Maria Manic & Penelope Ford  Faye, Willow, & Jordynne Grace VS Maria, Penelope, & Savannah Evans  Faye & Willow VS Sea Stars VS Brittany Blake & Samantha Heights
title: Sorry You're Watching This: Faye Jackson
